videos.headline: Arizona's Wilson pounds his way for TD
videos.description: Nick Wilson bullies his way in from 1-yard out in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Arizona's Green walks in for TD
videos.description: Zach Green scores the easy touchdown in the first quarter against the Beavers.

videos.headline: Arizona's Tate drags defenders for TD
videos.description: Wildcats QB Khalil Tate runs through and around defenders on his way to a 19-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Arizona's Taylor gashes the Oregon State defense for 56 yards
videos.description: J.J. Taylor sprints through the Beaver defense for a 56-yard gain in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Arizona's Ellison takes reverse 27 yards for TD
videos.description: Tony Ellison runs untouched 27 yards to the end zone putting the Wildcats up big before the half.

videos.headline: Rodriguez says he's happy with his QB's performance
videos.description: Arizona head coach Rich Rodriguez says that he's happy with the way Khalil Tate has responded, coming off an emotional loss to USC.

videos.headline: Oregon State's Togiai gets Beavers on the board
videos.description: Noah Togiai catches a 15-yard touchdown pass from Darell Garretson in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Oregon State's Hodgins makes NFL-style TD catch
videos.description: Isaiah Hodgins displays beautiful footwork to keep two feet in bounds in the corner of the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Arizona's Green scores second TD
videos.description: Zach Green runs into the end zone untouched for the second time as the Wildcats continue to dominate.

videos.headline: Oregon State's Garretson finds wide-open Hernandez for TD
videos.description: Beavers QB Darell Garretson finds WR Timmy Hernandez all alone in the end zone.

videos.headline: Oregon State's Nall takes screen 44 yards for TD
videos.description: Ryan Nall follows his blockers all the way to the end zone for the 44-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Rodriguez credits offensive line for record breaking rushing performance
videos.description: Arizona head coach Rich Rodriguez gives praise to his offensive line as the Wildcats rush for 534 yards and set a school record.

videos.headline: Arizona rushing attack dominates as Wildcats win big 49-28
videos.description: Rod Gilmore and Mark Jones break down Arizona's lethal rushing attack led by QB Khalil Tate.
